title: Metallica - And Justice For All (kick drum boost)
description:
I was bored today so I thought i&#039;d try and improve the kick drum sound on this album as we all know it&#039;s wasn&#039;t the best out of the studio. Certain combos might not sound as good as others and certain systems may still require some minor EQ adjustments. Basically the songs themselves now have a bit more "kick" in them which makes for a good base to start with.

Enjoy and please seed.
